title: Will I get my Ranked Rewards?
body:
Hey guys! Hey Riot Support!

I'm just curious, if I will receive my ranked rewards, since all my mates got them by now.
The thing is, I got chat restricted one week before the season ended, but informed myself and it said:
If you dont have an ACTIVE ban on season end (7/11/17 11:59pm), I will receive the rewards.

So I pushed all the games and the restirct was gone.
I am still locked on Honor rewards though

Any confirmation that I will the rewards?

Best regards
Thyrean

replies.body: No worries just yet, those ranked rewards are still being delivered. If you still don't see anything after a week or so, hit up your EUW agents in a ticket to see what might have gone wrong.
